   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">FORECAST LIST</uicontrol> page, by default, all approved forecast records are displayed. You can  view the  forecast distribution   of  budget estimate items.</context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the module menu, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Projects</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">PROJECTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the list page, double-click the required project, and in the navigation pane, expand the project folder.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the navigation pane, expand <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Budget Management</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Forecasts</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">FORECAST LIST</uicontrol> page is displayed.</info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the list page, select the appropriate forecast record, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">View</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">GENERAL DETAILS</uicontrol> page is displayed.</info>
            <info product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <title class="- topic/title ">General Details Page</title>
                  <image href="../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/Forecast_GnrlDetails.jpg"
                         class="- topic/image "
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </info>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">GENERAL DETAILS</uicontrol> page displays the following non-editable fields:<table colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
                  <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="30%" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="70%" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Field Name</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Description</entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">ID</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">An identification number of the forecast. </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Description</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The detailed description of the forecast.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Notes</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The notes on the forecast.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Start Date</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The   start date of the forecast.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">End Date</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The   end date of the forecast.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Created On</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The date on which the forecast is created.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Created By</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The name of the user who created this forecast.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Approved On</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The date  on which the record was approved.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Approved By</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The name of the approver.</entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </info>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">FORECAST DETAILS</uicontrol> page displays the following non-editable fields:<table colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
                  <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="30%" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="70%" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Column Name</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Description</entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Name</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Name of the forecast is displayed.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Start Date</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The  start date of the forecast.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">End Date</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The  end date of the forecast.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Duration </entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Based on the  start date and end date, the duration is displayed.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Curve</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Displays the distribution curve that is applied to the   budget. </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Unit</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">The unit for the item as defined in the budget estimate.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Amount in $</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Displays the total <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Amount in $</uicontrol> for each item from the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">CURRENT BUDGET ITEMS</uicontrol> page.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Remaining Amount in $</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">It is calculated as: Amount in $ - Sum of Amounts in Forecast<p class="- topic/p ">This helps the Project Manager understand if there is a overshoot or undershoot of the budget.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">&lt;&lt;Month Year&gt;&gt; </entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Displays  budget distribution  across  various months of the project. <p class="- topic/p ">You can toggle between the monthly or yearly view using the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Monthly View</uicontrol> and <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Yearly View</uicontrol> toolbar options, respectively.<note class="- topic/note "> The default cost distribution, as   monthly or yearly, is configured in the  <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Budget Management</uicontrol> page of the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Administration</uicontrol> module. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For more information, refer to <xref href="../../Administration/Functional_Configurations/CnfigBdgtMgmt.dita"
                                             class="- topic/xref "/>
                                    </ph>
                                 </note>
                              </p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </info>
         </step>
